  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
A 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_primary_care_network">Primary Care Network</xref>
 (<xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_primary_care_network">PCN</xref>) is an integral part of 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_nhs_england">NHS England</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
         <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_primary_care_network">Primary Care Networks</xref>
 were introduced into the National Health Service in England as part of the 
              <xref href="https://www.england.nhs.uk/long-term-plan/"
               scope="external"
               format="html">NHS Long Term Plan</xref>
 and form the building blocks of 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_integrated_care_system">Integrated Care Systems</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
A 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_primary_care_network">Primary Care Network</xref>
 consists of a group of 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_gp_practice">GP Practices</xref>
 working together with a range of local 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_health_care_provider">Health Care Providers</xref>
 (pharmacy, mental health, social care, community and voluntary sector).        </p>
      <p>
         <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_primary_care_network">Primary Care Networks</xref>
 build on the core of current primary care services and enable greater provision of proactive, personalised, coordinated and more integrated health and social care.        </p>
      <p>
For further information on 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_primary_care_network">Primary Care Networks</xref>, see the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_nhs_england">NHS England</xref>
 website at: 
              <xref href="https://www.england.nhs.uk/primary-care/primary-care-networks/"
               scope="external"
               format="html">Primary care networks</xref>.        </p>
  </div>
